 209:src/main.cpp  **** // ŌöĆŌöĆ Voice 4: clean sine organ / flute (a melodic, non-bass departure) ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌö
 210:src/main.cpp  **** //   Pure sine oscillators stacked like organ drawbars: octave-down body, root,
 211:src/main.cpp  **** //   octave-up air, plus a second osc tuned a hair sharp (1.005├Ś) for a slow,
 212:src/main.cpp  **** //   warm chorus shimmer instead of a chord. Higher register than the basses, a
 213:src/main.cpp  **** //   mostly-open clean filter, and just a touch of drive so pressure adds gentle
 214:src/main.cpp  **** //   harmonic warmth. Sines never alias, so it stays smooth all the way up.
