 636:src/main.cpp  **** // Find up to `maxf` fingers: repeatedly take the strongest remaining peak, and
 637:src/main.cpp  **** // if it's far enough from the peaks already found, record its centroid; then
 638:src/main.cpp  **** // zero a ┬▒2 window around it and look again. The first two peaks come out
 639:src/main.cpp  **** // identical to the old 2-finger detector, so the mono path is unchanged.
